Say what you want about Zodwa, but Mzansi loves her and now she will be tagging us along her daily shenanigans! The Zodwa wabantu reality show is coming onto our screens soon and will premiere on Moja Love TV. The kasi hustler has made a name for herself! From dancing Eyadini to becoming Africa’s rising star! The reality show is nothing short of drama and will allow Zodwa’s fans to see what she gets up to everyday; from her love life and to the alleged beef between her and Khanyi Mbau! After several delays with the airing of her reality show, Zodwa Wabantu has confirmed that the “uncensored” reality show will hit our screens on the 25th of May.  